This directory stores generated landing pages.
Each subdirectory is a separate landing page, named after the niche slug.

Example structure:
```
landing-pages/
├── invoice-automation/
│   ├── index.html
│   └── style.css
└── scheduling-tool/
    ├── index.html
    └── style.css
```

These files are committed to the repo and served via GitHub Pages.
